style is a 2006 telugu musical dance film written , and directed by raghava lawrence .   produced by larsco entertainments , the film starred prabhu deva , raghava lawrence , raja , kamalinee mukherjee , and charmme kaur in important roles , whilst chiranjeevi and nagarjuna in cameo appearance , the film 's soundtrack is composed by mani sharma , and as lawrence 's second directorial venture after the blockbuster mass .   the film was a box-office hit and has garnered the filmfare award for best choreography .   the film was subsequently dubbed into tamil as lakshyam .